data.description: Charming Gahanna ranch, great location! Corner lot to Stygler, fast & easy walk to schools, restaurants, bars, cnvnc store. 10 minute walk to Creekside! 3 BR, 1 bath and private back yard with 6ft cedar fence and patio-- new soft top gazebo with cover stays! Brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring in most of home! Filtered drinking water system. Fully insulated walls and attic, 1 car attached garage. Washer and dryer stay!
